{"tid":775570,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Apple 表明 iPhone 唔會竊聽用戶嘅對話，亦唔會將用戶嘅說話分享畀第三方","createTime":"2018-08-11T09:31:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-12T15:27:09.000Z","uid":1886,"like":18,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4bbbe85c502355a991341986e3640559b71d2064","tid":775570,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T09:31:54.000Z","msg":"Facebook 處理用戶個人資料的手法，引發美國以至全球各地用戶的關注，早前美國的眾議院能源和商業委員會向 Apple 去信，要求對方解釋手機和智能揚聲器等裝置，是否與外間傳聞般會竊聽用戶的對話。Apple 日前回應，明確表示 iPhone 並不會竊聽用戶的對話，亦不會將用戶的說話分享給第三方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/0810-4a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F0810-4a.jpg&h=0bd9d19c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/08/10/apple-confirms-iphone-doesnt-listen-conversations/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F08%2F10%2Fapple-confirms-iphone-doesnt-listen-conversations%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=xKNbBR6N07RB1atn6mjNiACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=f119887d\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/08/10/apple-confirms-iphone-doesnt-listen-conversations/mobile-phone/</a></div>"},{"pid":"22819d440feca1c899ca3eee3ba6754f054fd98c","tid":775570,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T09:32:21.000Z","msg":"Apple 在信中指顧客並非他們的產品，他們的商業模式並非以收集大量個人資料並銷售予廣告業界，這無疑是指桑罵槐向競爭對手作出攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。Apple 澄清 iPhone 並不會竊聽用戶的日常對話，iPhone 的語音識別器只會聆聽用戶的「Hey Siri」致令。當 Siri 被喚醒，它會確認用戶是否有意使用，而用戶發問的內容都會和一個隨機產生的裝置識別碼連結，但不會連結 Apple ID，用戶只需將 Siri 和字典功能關閉，重開後隨機產生的裝置識別碼就會作出變更。"},{"pid":"874aa445fb1ca6ec02cc2dbd7358941b8890d562","tid":775570,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T09:32:56.000Z","msg":"Apple 在回信中又提到，位置資料並不會和用戶的名字或 Apple ID 掛鈎，亦不會利用位置資料播放廣告。Apple 強調用戶有自主權決定是非使用定位功能，亦要求所有 Apps 在安裝或運行時向用戶索取使用位置資料的權限。Apple 表示相信私隱是基本人權，在設計產品和服務時都會盡可能減少收集用戶的資料。不過 Apple 不會，亦無法監控開發者如何處理收集到的用戶數據，亦無法預防他們轉移數據。"},{"pid":"54955b335b5b97227dc69fac2a5d25b5cd7ce9ae","tid":775570,"uid":164092,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T10:28:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zBnDWSvaQ1I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzBnDWSvaQ1I&d=xKNbBR6N07RB1atn6mjNiACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=e3bf0b6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zBnDWSvaQ1I</a><br />\nGoogle is Always Hearing You<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a309a61b373bd9ff9d508e31035e6e3bf12e43c9","tid":775570,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T12:35:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bf09efbceb6c44370ef6a3edb1d001618e632f0","tid":775570,"uid":143582,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T14:13:52.000Z","msg":"其他公司產品咁平咪就係平係呢度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67be79687365a03bb75289b9b77fe7460a6833ee","tid":775570,"uid":187776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T14:16:41.000Z","msg":"，Apple<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e63097040df2c5a5825153b72eefac4d21e7c81","tid":775570,"uid":164092,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"7bf09efbceb6c44370ef6a3edb1d001618e632f0","tid":775570,"uid":143582,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T14:13:52.000Z","msg":"其他公司產品咁平咪就係平係呢度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T14:22:54.000Z","msg":"其實Apple賺好多"},{"pid":"fecf95cd093473df31fbe0aa401bdfff8c84f9a0","tid":775570,"uid":36822,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4