\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a68258df1da16b332efbaab8064517f19174b06","tid":775570,"uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c232f153ecbbadff0bb36f35faf61aa07ff29481","tid":775570,"uid":55597,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T00:20:28.000Z","msg":"apple: iphone 唔會偷野<br />\n中國：人權最好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T05:53:53.000Z","msg":"Google 重返中國，受中國監管，唔通你又話Google 奶共啦喎<br />\n<br />\n你生喺一個極權國家，就係無人權咖啦，想中國有人權，一係「共同建設民主中國」，一係移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aad534cae63dbc6130db8e5e7eaa1de54c3cf21","tid":775570,"uid":12628,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ad73bbc40b29589db29ffdb16181a9ebb1ffed44","tid":775570,"uid":1886,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"e6b4d4bd48f852f7ea7921a862de7fd981aa029b","tid":775570,"uid":158977,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4e63097040df2c5a5825153b72eefac4d21e7c81","tid":775570,"uid":164092,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T14:22:54.000Z","msg":"其實Apple賺好多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T16:24:27.000Z","msg":"因為成本低 價高 都仲有咁多on9買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T05:50:57.000Z","msg":"A11 研發成本低？<br />\n<br />\niPhone 硬件勁對手咁多<br />\n<br />\n個價都係同對手旗鼓相當咋...<br />\n<br />\n究竟邊個成本低、價高呢可<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T05:58:26.000Z","msg":"呢啲垃圾港豬，一方面要開源，免費，叫佢為開源貢獻下，不了，唔識it,要炒賣。<br />\n叫佢比錢研發或買app,不了，要破解，唔好比錢人賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9831f633c7ab9cd14417368bf84017bfd2832856","tid":775570,"uid":68094,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T06:25:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"24e44bb18e6b76ceabd516da35da1df8a34dc17d","tid":775570,"uid":125365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T06:35:18.000Z","msg":"they are using whats called differential privacy in cryptography<br />\n<br />\nit's better to address that they still actively collecting data from user, just like many others do<br />\n<br />\ntypically the collection activities are included with their terms, so technically they are not 'spying' on anyone although in effect they do, in a different scale, depends on their business model<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Differential_Privacy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FDifferential_Privacy&d=xKNbBR6N07RB1atn6mjNiACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=069cc2ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Differential_Privacy</a><br />\n<br />\nthe common practice/trick is spying through subsidiaries application/3rd party injected cookies(sometimes unconfigurable to reject from browser application), so anyone can claim their company is doing the most for user's privacy"},{"pid":"62b71a8030933a1c5008e3fdfc982ee235ddb333","tid":775570,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54955b335b5b97227dc69fac2a5d25b5cd7ce9ae","tid":775570,"uid":164092,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T10:28:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zBnDWSvaQ1I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzBnDWSvaQ1I&d=xKNbBR6N07RB1atn6mjNiACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=e3bf0b6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zBnDWSvaQ1I</a><br />\nGoogle is Always Hearing You<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T08:02:39.000Z","msg":"個research 有問題，佢開youtube live + 字幕，咁同真接叫google 「你聽我啦」有乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54d4398afebb14b2b77936af38a272c715155940","tid":775570,"uid":16